course_title: Intensive Chamber Ensemble - INT CHMB ENS

sections.comments: MUSC 169 represents credit for the extra work that some students do in some ensembles and should involve 1 hr/week additional coaching time. Permission to take 169 must come from the division coordinator (via a signed drop/add form forwarded to the MUSC student advisor) who will coach you in either 160 or 162, because 169  has 160 or 162 as a co-requisite (as 169 represents "extra work" you are doing in 160 or 162).  Not for use by pianists.  Hand in course add form to Music Student Advisor (music.advisor@ubc.ca)
